<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Symfony E-Commerce</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #4a6cf7;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #777;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #4a6cf7;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .feature {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .feature h3 {
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Welcome to Symfony E-Commerce!</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear {{ user.firstName }} {{ user.lastName }},</p>
            
            <p>Thank you for creating an account with Symfony E-Commerce! We're excited to have you join our community.</p>
            
            <p>With your new account, you can:</p>
            
            <div class="feature">
                <h3>Shop with Ease</h3>
                <p>Browse our wide selection of products and enjoy a seamless shopping experience.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="feature">
                <h3>Track Your Orders</h3>
                <p>Keep track of your orders and view your order history at any time.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="feature">
                <h3>Save Your Favorites</h3>
                <p>Save your favorite products for quick access later.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="feature">
                <h3>Get Exclusive Offers</h3>
                <p>Receive notifications about special promotions and exclusive offers.</p>
            </div>
            
            <p>We're committed to providing you with the best shopping experience possible. If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to contact our customer service team.</p>
            
            <p>Happy shopping!</p>
            
            <p>Best regards,<br>
            The Symfony E-Commerce Team</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; {{ "now"|date("Y") }} Symfony E-Commerce. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>This email was sent to {{ user.email }}</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
